Nor-Quest ResourcesInc said it will make a takeover offer to acquire all shares ofNorthair Mines Ltd on the basis of one Nor-Quest share plus onedlr for two shares of Northair.    Nor-Quest said it plans to bring Northair's Willa Mine inthe Nelson area of British Columbia into production usingNor-Quest's recently acquired 1200-ton per day mill located inthe area. Reuter&#3;